Title: Jung Pumpen Jung Pumpen drainage pumps U3 KS 4m 1 phase automatic submersible pump
Description: Incorporating safe EIP technology, this Jung Pumpen U3KS centrifugal submersible pump is suitable for stationary or portable use. With an integrated flushing device to reduce deposits and integrated low-level pumping, which means less risk of flooding, this pump can remove rainwater, lightly polluted water and waste water from domestic dishwashers and washing machines. It can be used in high temperature water, however U3KS is not suitable for urinal or lavatory effluent. When used as a stationary appliance, this submersible pump is commonly employed to remove water from drains in cellars, laundries or storerooms and also offers protection from flooding. Ready to install straight out of the box, U3KS is fitted using the GR 32 guide rail system for simpler maintenance down the line.

Title: Grundfos Unilift unilift submersible pump automatic
Description: A single stage submersible pump, Grundfos Unilift CC pumps clean, non-aggressive water and grey wastewater with pumping down to 3mm water level and automatic operation. This pump has a top and a side outlet for easy fitting to existing pipework and is suitable for either stationary or portable use, allowing free passage of particles up to 10mm. Unilift's motor incorporates automatic overload protection, cutting out in case of overload and restarting automatically when cooled.

Title: Jung Pumpen 1phase automatic corrosion resistant pump
Description: Suitable for stationary or portable use, this Jung Pumpen U6KES drainage pump can be used for mildly contaminated waste and ground water, in sumps with rain water, drainage or seepage water, silage liquor and for liquid manure. Thanks to a high quality mechanical seal, it can also extract abrasive media. In stationary use, U6K ES is ideal for removing waste water from domestic appliances such as dishwashers and washing machines.

Title: Jung Pumpen Sumo US73HES 1 phase high temperature floor mouted unit with pump
Description: The Jung Pumpen Sumo heavy duty centrifugal submersible drainage pump deals with very contaminated water and can handle stone-free solids of up to 30mm particle size. Usable wherever wastewater up to 194°F (90°C) is involved, such as in laundries, or in industrial dishwashers and washing machines or for the emergency overflow of heating systems, this pump is designed for stationary use and incorporates a controllable oil chamber, wear-resistant mechanical seal and integrated winding thermostats for a long operational life.

Title: Jung Pumpen Drainmaster 1phase drainage station fitted with pump
Description: Offering all the convenience of a complete pumping station in a compact package, the Jung Pumpen Drainmaster single phase drainage station with pump is built around a 26L (approx.) plastic tank, which is suitable for floor or wall mounting. The station includes an inlet sleeve for 40mm PVC/HT tubing above and three inlets to its sides.
